  "query": "-- rows ที่ paid_at = พ.ย. 2024 แต่ created_at ไม่ใช่ พ.ย. 2024\nSELECT external_id, contract_no, paid_at, amount, created_by, created_at\nFROM payment_transactions\nWHERE section = 'ff365' \n  AND paid_at BETWEEN '2024-11-01' AND '2024-11-30'\n  AND (created_at IS NULL OR created_at NOT LIKE '2024-11%')\nORDER BY created_at DESC\nLIMIT 20;",
